-- Russia's Magnit sales rise 30.5 pct in April y/y
-- 
-- Thu May 08, 2014 02:10AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, May 8 (Reuters) - Russia's biggest food retailer, Magnit <MGNT.MM> <MGNTq.L>, said on Thursday its sales increased 30.5 percent in April year-on-year, accelerating from 24.5 percent in March.

Magnit said sales amounted to 59.7 billion roubles ($1.69 billion) last month when it opened 87 new stores, bringing its total to 8,343.